oozham ( english : chance ) is a 2016 indian malayalam-language action drama film written and directed by jeethu joseph . the film stars prithviraj sukumaran , neeraj madhav , divya pillai and debutant rasna pavithran in the lead roles . shamdat sainudheen handled the cinematography . oozham revolves around a demolition expert who teams up with his fiancee and friend to avenge the deaths of their family members from the ceo of a pharmaceutical company who got them killed . the film released on 8 september 2016 . oozham grossed more than 15 crores from kerala boxoffice and 30 cr from worldwide boxoffice thereby becoming a super hit .